title: Ceres Natural Foods
description: Vegetarian store stocking also vegan and gluten-free products, from supplements, aromatherapy, and homeopathic remedies to eco friendly cleaners, bodycare, and cosmetics, to locally made organic wines, beers, and spirits and a homebrew section with kits. It's been in the wholefood store business since 1976 and produces its own branded ranges of conventional and organic dried fruits, nuts, seeds, pulses, grains, flours, herbs and spices.
